window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A war is on the horizon for the kingdom of Prost.</p> <p>But for those from Krader, their lives were already turned upside down amidst the Collapse.</p> <p>Reeling from his loss and unsure what to do next, Terrence will need to refocus to earn his first Rank as a Dungeoneer.</p> <p>For everyone else, recruitment for the war is bringing the kingdom to its knees.</p> <p>Trying his best to stay out of the conflict, Tom is eager to reunite with his friends and family in the Capital.</p> <p>Storylines converge as everyone's Affinities progress further every day.</p> <p>Will Tom be able to help Terrence and his friends reach new heights? Or will the stress of war cause everyone to crash and burn?</p>"; 
